- No `eval` / `Function` constructor usage.
- No `child_process` / shell execution.
- No SQL queries (so no injection risk here).
- No `res.send(userInput)` reflections (no XSS surface in current code).
- No prototype pollution sinks.
- No unsafe deserialization.
- No path traversal surface (no `fs` / `res.sendFile`).

